127
00:06:50,314 --> 00:06:54,875
And kind of as a result of the focus being on that easy relationship versus something more rigorous,

128
00:06:55,375 --> 00:06:57,755
a lot of production nuance ended up left unspoken.

129
00:06:58,335 --> 00:07:00,817
