there was this assumed shared understanding

132
00:07:05,979 --> 00:07:07,440
based on a general sense of alignment,

133
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,661
but there were no actual processes

134
00:07:09,981 --> 00:07:12,222
to determine or ratify that alignment.

135
